text: Schuylkill County is a county in the U.S. state of Pennsylvania. Its county seat is Pottsville. In 2020, 143,049 people lived in Schuylkill. == History == The county was created on March 1, 1811.http://www.phmc.state.pa.us/bah/dam/rg/di/IncorporationDatesForMunicipalities/pdfs/schuylkill.pdf?catid=54 == References == Category:1810s establishments in Pennsylvania Category:1811 establishments in the United States Category:Pennsylvania counties
title: Schuylkill County, Pennsylvania
